Paper: hep-th/9607146

Date: 1996-07-17

Title: Relic gravitons from the pre-big bang

knowAuthors: M. Gasperini

Comments: 34 pages, LATEX, 12 figures included using epsf. See also

I discuss the status of present knowledge about a possible background ofrelic gravitons left by an early, pre-big bang cosmological epoch, whoseexistence in the past of our Universe is suggested by the duality symmetries ofstring theory.